<div id="post-262147" class="blog-post position-2 even-post"><div class="even-post-inner blog-post-inner"><h1 class="title"><a href="http://softwarelivre.org/perl/blog/yapc-brasil-2010">YAPC::Brasil 2010</a></h1><span class="publishing-info"><span class="date">Ottobre 21, 2010 0:00</span><span class="author">, by Software Livre Brasil</span><span class="comments"> - <a href="/perl/blog/yapc-brasil-2010#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>no comments yet</span></a></span></span><div class="event-card">
